Question: One of the pictures has a species that isn't a type of ray.

Reference Answer: False

Right image URL: http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_Z3u9Ki2Nw3c/SwiVMPoou2I/AAAAAAAABdA/aABKRQ-rezg/s1600/raya_dasyatis_pastinaca.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the species in the image a type of ray?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the species in the image a type of ray?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} xor {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
